    "However, it may be difficult to integrate the domain knowledge into AI techniques due to the different design ideas.",
    "Data securityRecently, data security has received increased attention, and the ISAC system can collect the sensitive information of users, which requires effective mechanisms to prevent information leakage and ensure data security.",
    "However, training an AI model on the data containing sensitive information increases the risk of leakage because the AI model is vulnerable to adversarial attacks, and some attacks can obtain the sensitive information of the users through reverse engineering [284].",
    "Therefore, it is very important to ensure the data security of AI-enabled ISAC systems.",
    "Although the unique training mechanism of FL can guarantee data security as discussed in Subsection 4.4, the frequent model update over wireless channels makes FL vulnerable to various attacks such as eavesdropping."
